{
  "stem": "1603.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] because maybe I'm thinking of her a lot, maybe because she was only person who just sent love towards me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so that was something, an interesting thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because in life-- because in life, you meet people and then you fall in love and then later on disappointments start coming and-- because nobody's perfect and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then relationships weaken, marriages are breaking up, like mine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And with her, there was nothing like that because that's the only experience we had is just this one writing experience.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not know where she-- who she was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it-- maybe it's not too late to-- to do a search.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And naturally, I still see her as a certain, you know, girl in my mind, because I cannot accept that-- my mind cannot accept 52 years which went by.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the school was a very good school, very interesting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I learned a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that was just a matter of chance, and heaven knows why those little ink holders were empty and they were there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe-- it could been that maybe not in every space people were sitting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And only maybe they filled up the places with ink where somebody was sitting and writing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe Robbie pulled it out himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that detail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I just remember the fact that he had these empties around him and he was clowning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's when my mind started working and doing this thing towards him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister is about 2 and 1/2 years older than I am.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So basically I lived a very lonely life as a child, because my sister was a very attractive young lady.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
